Package com.codeborne.selenide.impl

Class StaticConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codeborne.selenide.impl.StaticConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Config
    public class StaticConfig
extends java.lang.Object
implements Config
    A non-static facade for static fields in Configuration It was created only to keep backward compatibility in Selenide 5.0.0: every time when somebody modifies, say, Configuration.timeout, it will immediately reflect in timeout() This class should not be normally used in end user's code.
